K

KEEP_ALL - Enum constant in enum org.omg.dds.core.policy.History.Kind
On the publishing side, the Service will attempt to keep all samples (representing each value written) of each instance of data (identified by its key) managed by the DataWriter until they can be delivered to all subscribers.
KEEP_LAST - Enum constant in enum org.omg.dds.core.policy.History.Kind
On the publishing side, the Service will only attempt to keep the most recent "depth" samples (History.getDepth()) of each instance of data (identified by its key) managed by the DataWriter.
